## Code Walkthrough

Here is a correct implementation of this feature in JavaScript:

```javascript
// Factorial calculation recursively
function factorial(n) {
  if (n <= 1) {
    return 1;
  }
  return n * factorial(n - 1);
}

console.log(factorial(3));
```

